(160, 6, '2016-02-09 11:04:03', '2016-02-09 10:04:03', '<div id="ember636" class="ember-view markdown">\r\n\r\nTriggered after a parent item is linked to a child item.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="methods">\r\n	<li>AfterLinkParent( ChildItem, ParentItem );</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe arguments in this list consist of:\r\n<ul class="arguments">\r\n	<li>ChildItem of type Item: The child item.</li>\r\n	<li>ParentItem of type Item or Meeting: The parent item or parent meeting.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'AfterLinkParent', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'afterlinkparent', '', '', '2016-02-15 12:14:36', '2016-02-15 11:14:36', '', 0, 'http://devcenter.tenforce.com/portal/?post_type=events&#038;p=160', 0, 'events', '', 0),
