(202, 6, '2016-02-09 14:35:52', '2016-02-09 13:35:52', 'These are the most commonly used standard fields (SF):\n<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW " data-enlighter-language="csharp">Nr = 1,\nTitle = 2,\nAssignedTo = 4,\nDueDate = 5,\nStatus = 7,\nPriority = 8,\nPlannedStartDate = 16,\nList = 19,\nOriginator = 21,\nTags = 22,\nDescription = 23,\nCreator = 24,\nCreatedOn = 25,\nClosedOn = 39,\nActualStartDate = 40,\nActualDueDate = 41,\nRootItem = 112, //The given item with all children and grandchildren\nChild = 113, //Only the children of the given item\nItemId = 114,\nAssignedUsergroups = 115</pre>\nHere is the complete list of all IDs of the standard fields with their code and type of field.\n\nFieldId Code Type\nSF1 Nr Text\nSF2 Title Text\nSF3 OverviewTab Tab\nSF4 Assigned to SingleSelect\nSF5 Due date Date\nSF6 Due text Text\nSF7 Status SingleSelect\nSF8 Priority SingleSelect\nSF9 Application SingleSelect\nSF10 Found in SingleSelect\nSF11 Solved in SingleSelect\nSF12 Source event Text\nSF13 Source date Date\nSF14 Performed By SingleSelect\nSF15 Performed For SingleSelect\nSF16 PlannedStartDate Date\nSF17 Planned effort (hours) Number\nSF18 Actual effort (hours) Number\nSF19 List SingleSelect\nSF20 ETC Number\nSF21 Originator SingleSelect\nSF22 Tags MultiSelect\nSF23 Description BigText\nSF24 Creator SingleSelect\nSF25 Created On Date\nSF26 LastUpdatedBy SingleSelect\nSF27 LastUpdatedOn Date\nSF28 SolutionTab Tab\nSF29 Solution BigText\nSF30 InternalCommentTab Tab\nSF31 ChildItemsTab Tab\nSF32 CommentsTab Tab\nSF33 AttachmentsTab Number of attachments\nSF34 HistoryTab Tab\nSF35 Impact SingleSelect\nSF36 Probability SingleSelect\nSF37 Mitigation Impact SingleSelect\nSF38 Mitigation Probability SingleSelect\nSF39 Closed On Date\nSF40 ActualStartDate Date\nSF41 Actual due date Date\nSF42 Bill Type SingleSelect\nSF43 Activity SingleSelect\nSF44 Account Code SingleSelect\nSF45 Comment Type SingleSelect\nSF46 Cause SingleSelect\nSF47 MeetingMinutesTab Tab\nSF48 MeetingMinutes