(171, 6, '2016-02-09 11:31:58', '2016-02-09 10:31:58', '<div id="ember636" class="ember-view markdown">\r\n\r\nTriggered after validation of the item fields during creating and updating an item, this validation includes the check to see that all mandatory fields are filled in.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="methods">\r\n	<li>AfterValidation( OldItem, NewItem );</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe arguments in this list consist of:\r\n<ul class="arguments">\r\n	<li>OldItem of type Item: Item in the state before the change. (null when creating a new item)</li>\r\n	<li>NewItem of type Item: Item in the state after the change.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'AfterValidation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aftervalidation', '', '', '2016-02-15 11:42:27', '2016-02-15 10:42:27', '', 0, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/?post_type=events&#038;p=171', 0, 'events', '', 0),
(172, 6, '2016-02-09 11:39:56', '2016-02-09 10:39:56', '<div id="ember636" class="ember-view markdown">\r\n\r\nThis event is the same as the AfterValidation event, except that it is only triggered when creating a new item.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class="methods">\r\n	<li>AfterValidationOnCreate( OldItem, NewItem );</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe arguments in this list consist of:\r\n<ul class="arguments">\r\n	<li>OldItem of type Item: Always null.</li>\r\n	<li>NewItem of type Item: Item in the state after the change.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'AfterValidationOnCreate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aftervalidationoncreate', '', '', '2016-02-15 11:42:20', '2016-02-15 10:42:20', '', 0, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/?post_type=events&#038;p=172', 0, 'events', '', 0),
