(248, 6, '2016-02-15 16:13:16', '2016-02-15 15:13:16', 'This is how it can be done:\n<pre>//get comboBoxParameter\nvar combBoxParameterId = (string)(ScriptContext.ScriptParameters.GetParameter(&quot;ComboBoxparameter&quot;));\n//get comboBoxParameterLovs\nvar combBoxParameterLovs = Api.FormulaParameterValues.Read(combBoxParameterId );\nif (combBoxParameterLovs == null)\n   throw new ScriptException(&quot;(combBoxParameterLovs == null&quot;);\n//Use code of the LOV (e.g. to set the list)\nitemFh.SetString(c.sf.List, combBoxParameterLovs.Name);</pre>', 'How to get the code of a value (LOV) of a &#8216;ComboBox&#8217; parameter of an Action Button?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-to-get-the-code-of-a-value-lov-of-a-combobox-parameter-of-an-action-button', '', '', '2016-02-15 16:13:16', '2016-02-15 15:13:16', '', 239, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/questions/question/how-to-get-the-code-of-a-value-lov-of-a-combobox-parameter-of-an-action-button/?show_answer=248#answer_248', 0, 'answer', '', 0) ;
