(277, 6, '2016-02-16 16:19:51', '2016-02-16 15:19:51', '<pre>// TODO: Provide parent item and create a new child item\nItem parent = ...;\nItem child = ...;\n// Link child to parent\nvar handler = new FieldHandler(child);\nif (child.Parent == null)\n  child.Parent = new Item { Id = parent.Id };\nelse\n  child.Parent.Id = parent.Id;\n// Save child item\nhandler.Save();</pre>', 'How to link a child and parent item to each other?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-to-link-a-child-and-parent-item-to-each-other', '', '', '2016-02-16 16:20:03', '2016-02-16 15:20:03', '', 276, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/questions/question/how-to-link-a-child-and-parent-item-to-each-other/?show_answer=277#answer_277', 0, 'answer', '', 0),
