(429, 36, '2016-04-08 15:28:36', '2016-04-08 14:28:36', 'The same can be achieved with less code when the common add-in is used:\n<pre>var query = Pmx.Items(FieldRetriever)\n    .Where(SF.List, f =&gt; f.Equals(list))\n    .Where(SF.Nr, f =&gt; f.Equals(&quot;5515&quot;))\n    .Select(SF.Title, SF.Status);\nvar result = query.Execute();</pre>\nNote that there are various other kinds of matching, such as <em>StartsWith</em>, <em>Contains</em>, <em>EndsWith</em>, NotEquals, <em>Between</em>, :\n<pre>var query = Pmx.Items(FieldRetriever)\n    .Where(SF.List, f =&gt; f.Equals(listid))\n    .Where(SF.Nr, f =&gt; f.StartsWith(&quot;55&quot;))\n    .Where(SF.CreatedOn, f =&gt; f.Between(date1, date2))\n    .Select(SF.Title, SF.Nr);</pre>', 'How to use exact matching in an itemfilter', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '427-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-08 15:28:36', '2016-04-08 14:28:36', '', 427, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/427-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
