(579, 3, '2016-05-17 11:23:15', '2016-05-17 10:23:15', 'Thanks. I\'ve tried to access the online help for Tracker, with following URL:\n\nhttps://texectracker.tenforce.com/Pages/OnlineHelp/default/en/index.html\n\nHowever, it gives me a 404.\n\nAm I missing something?', 'How do I consume Tracker info using OData?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-consume-tracker-info-using-odata-2', '', '', '2016-05-17 11:23:15', '2016-05-17 10:23:15', '', 575, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/questions/question/how-do-i-consume-tracker-info-using-odata/?show_answer=579#answer_579', 0, 'answer', '', 0),
(580, 25, '2016-05-19 07:05:43', '2016-05-19 06:05:43', 'that\'s because the tracker application is not installed in the root (Default Website)\n\nyou need:https://texectracker.tenforce.com/texectracker/Pages/OnlineHelp/default/en/index.html or just use the magnifier icon in the upper right corner.', 'How do I consume Tracker info using OData?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-consume-tracker-info-using-odata-3', '', '', '2016-05-19 07:05:43', '2016-05-19 06:05:43', '', 575, 'http://tenforce.konstantinkharlov.com/questions/question/how-do-i-consume-tracker-info-using-odata/?show_answer=580#answer_580', 0, 'answer', '', 0),
